title: PMLN’ candidate Tariq Fazal Chaudhary wins NA-47 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz Tariq Fazal Chaudhary has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-47, Islamabad II by securing 10,2502 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent Candidate Mohammad Shaoaib Shaheen, who bagged 86,396 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 58.80 percent.
